			<pubDate>Tue, 15 Mar 2016 19:48:56 GMT</pubDate>
			<description><![CDATA[So I debated sharing this for awhile since this is a mostly anonymous forum.  -Though I, like many here have been a member of the community since the early 2000's. 
 
But the pics I just got from my cardiologist are just too cool not to share, heh.  I find them pretty amazing at least. 
 
